“‘Mr. Radney, I will not obey you. Take that hammer away, or look to 
yourself.’ But the predestinated mate coming still closer to him, where the 
Lakeman stood fixed, now shook the heavy hammer within an inch of his teeth; 
meanwhile repeating a string of insufferable maledictions. Retreating not the 
thousandth part of an inch; stabbing him in the eye with the unflinching 
